      <title>scoop，oh-my-posh安装及使用</title>
      <link href="/2024/08/13/scoop%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/"/>
      <url>/2024/08/13/scoop%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>安装scoop并配置，安装oh-my-posh并配置</p><h4 id="要点"><a href="#要点" class="headerlink" title="要点"></a>要点</h4><ul><li>   微软商店先下载<code>powershell</code>（自带的太旧了）</li><li>   自备梯子</li></ul><h3 id="安装scoop"><a href="#安装scoop" class="headerlink" title="安装scoop"></a>安装scoop</h3><h4 id="设置powershell脚本执行权限："><a href="#设置powershell脚本执行权限：" class="headerlink" title="设置powershell脚本执行权限："></a>设置<code>powershell</code>脚本执行权限：</h4><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Set-ExecutionPolicy</span> <span class="literal">-ExecutionPolicy</span> RemoteSigned <span class="literal">-Scope</span> CurrentUser</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>默认安装位置为<code>_%USERPROFILE%\scoop_</code><br>如若自定义安装位置需设置环境变量,无需改变则直接_跳过此步_直接安装</p></blockquote><h5 id="1-设置用户安装路径"><a href="#1-设置用户安装路径" class="headerlink" title="1. 设置用户安装路径"></a>1. 设置用户安装路径</h5>  <figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$env:SCOOP</span>=<span class="string">&#x27;D:\Scoop&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="type">Environment</span>]::SetEnvironmentVariable(<span class="string">&#x27;SCOOP&#x27;</span>, <span class="variable">$env:SCOOP</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;User&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="2-使用管理员权限终端powershell设置全局安装路径"><a href="#2-使用管理员权限终端powershell设置全局安装路径" class="headerlink" title="2. 使用管理员权限终端powershell设置全局安装路径"></a>2. 使用管理员权限终端<code>powershell</code>设置全局安装路径</h5>  <figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable">$env:SCOOP_GLOBAL</span>=<span class="string">&#x27;D:\Scoop_Global&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="type">Environment</span>]::SetEnvironmentVariable(<span class="string">&#x27;SCOOP_GLOBAL&#x27;</span>, <span class="variable">$env:SCOOP_GLOBAL</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;Machine&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="打开终端powershell，键入如下，回车安装；"><a href="#打开终端powershell，键入如下，回车安装；" class="headerlink" title="打开终端powershell，键入如下，回车安装；"></a>打开终端<code>powershell</code>，键入如下，回车安装；</h4><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">iwr</span> <span class="literal">-useb</span> get.scoop.sh | <span class="built_in">iex</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="开始配置"><a href="#开始配置" class="headerlink" title="开始配置"></a>开始配置</h3><h4 id="scoop开始使用需要安装git，scoop安装的git我不会配外置OpenSSH，所以我手动下载安装版git"><a href="#scoop开始使用需要安装git，scoop安装的git我不会配外置OpenSSH，所以我手动下载安装版git" class="headerlink" title="scoop开始使用需要安装git，scoop安装的git我不会配外置OpenSSH，所以我手动下载安装版git"></a><code>scoop</code>开始使用需要安装<code>git</code>，scoop安装的<code>git</code>我不会配外置<code>OpenSSH</code>，所以我手动下载安装版<a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win"><code>git</code></a></h4><blockquote><p>记得选择<code>_Use external OpenSSH_</code></p></blockquote><h4 id="scoop执行更新"><a href="#scoop执行更新" class="headerlink" title="scoop执行更新"></a><code>scoop</code>执行更新</h4>  <figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="添加官方bucket和第三方bucket"><a href="#添加官方bucket和第三方bucket" class="headerlink" title="添加官方bucket和第三方bucket"></a>添加官方<code>bucket</code>和第三方<code>bucket</code></h4>  <figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop bucket add extras</span><br><span class="line">scoop bucket add apps https://github.com/kkzzhizhou/scoop<span class="literal">-apps</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>同时官方还提供<code>versions</code>,<code>nirsoft </code>,<code>java</code>这些<code>bucket</code>，可以自行添加</p></blockquote><h4 id="安装软件"><a href="#安装软件" class="headerlink" title="安装软件"></a>安装软件</h4><p>  首先安装<code>scoop-search</code>，可以改善<code>scoop search</code>的搜索体验<br>  安装aria2，提高下载速度<br>  安装adb工具，scrcpy手机投屏工具<br>  安装oh-my-posh，powershell美化工具 等</p>  <figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop install main/scoop<span class="literal">-search</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop install main/aria2</span><br><span class="line">scoop install main/adb</span><br><span class="line">scoop install main/scrcpy</span><br><span class="line">scoop install main/<span class="built_in">oh</span><span class="literal">-my-posh</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop install main/<span class="built_in">curl</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop install main/<span class="built_in">wget</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop install main/mihomo</span><br><span class="line">scoop install main/dnslookup</span><br><span class="line">scoop install extras/vscode</span><br><span class="line">scoop install main/ffmpeg</span><br><span class="line">scoop install extras/tsukimi</span><br><span class="line">scoop install main/rclone</span><br><span class="line">scoop install extras/obs<span class="literal">-studio</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop install main/grep</span><br><span class="line">scoop install apps/pixpin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p><code>scoop</code>常用命令</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;scoop update<span class="comment">#更新bucket数据</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop update &lt;PACKAGE_NAME&gt;<span class="comment">#更新软件</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop update *<span class="comment">#更新所有软件</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop status<span class="comment">#查看软件更新状态</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop install &lt;PACKAGE_NAME&gt;<span class="comment">#安装软件包</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop install &lt;BUCKET_NAME&gt;/&lt;PACKAGE_NAME&gt;<span class="comment">#安装特定bucket的软件</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop uninstall &lt;PACKAGE_NAME&gt;<span class="comment">#卸载软件</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop cacha show<span class="comment">#查看scoop缓存</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop cacha <span class="built_in">rm</span> &lt;PACKAGE_NAME&gt;<span class="comment">#移除某个软件的缓存</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop cacha <span class="built_in">rm</span> *<span class="comment">#清除所有缓存</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop bucket add &lt;BUCKET_NAME&gt;<span class="comment">#新增bucket（scoop内置bucket才能使用）</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop bucket add &lt;PACKAGE_NAME&gt; &lt;BUCKET_REPO_URL&gt;<span class="comment">#新增bucket</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop bucket <span class="built_in">rm</span> &lt;BUCKET_NAME&gt;<span class="comment">#删除bucket</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop search &lt;PACKAGE_NAME&gt;<span class="comment">#在所有bucket中搜索软件（安装scoop-search后，使用scoop-search取而代之</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop info &lt;PACKAGE_NAME&gt;<span class="comment">#查看某个软件包的信息</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;scoop config &#123;OPTIONS&#125;<span class="comment">#设置scoop</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></blockquote><h4 id="配置scoop使用aria2下载"><a href="#配置scoop使用aria2下载" class="headerlink" title="配置scoop使用aria2下载"></a>配置<code>scoop</code>使用aria2下载</h4>  <figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scoop config aria2<span class="literal">-enabled</span> True</span><br><span class="line">scoop config aria2<span class="operator">-split</span> <span class="number">32</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop config aria2<span class="literal">-max-connection-per-server</span> <span class="number">16</span></span><br><span class="line">scoop config aria2<span class="literal">-min-split-size</span> <span class="number">1</span>M</span><br><span class="line">scoop config aria2<span class="literal">-option</span> <span class="literal">--disable-ipv6</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="配置oh-my-posh"><a href="#配置oh-my-posh" class="headerlink" title="配置oh-my-posh"></a>配置oh-my-posh</h4><ol><li>下载安装nerd字体，比如<a href="https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts/releases/download/v3.3.0/Meslo.zip"><code>MesloLG Nerd Font</code></a>，并安装<blockquote><p>使用oh-my-posh自带的<code>oh-my-posh font install</code>可能会出现明明已安装字体，并且终端字体设置选项栏也有，但是却提示无字体的状况</p></blockquote></li><li>终端外观设置中选择你安装的Nerd字体</li><li>使用以下指令创建配置文件</li></ol><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">New-Item</span> <span class="literal">-Path</span> <span class="variable">$PROFILE</span> <span class="literal">-Type</span> File <span class="literal">-Force</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>随后打开配置文件</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">notepad <span class="variable">$PROFILE</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>写入</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">oh</span><span class="literal">-my-posh</span> init pwsh | <span class="built_in">Invoke-Expression</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以使用<code>Get-PoshThemes</code>实时查看可使用的主题，随后按提示写入<code>$PROFILE</code>，上文添加的<code>scoop-search</code>也需要在这里加入到&#96;$PROFIL中去，例如</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">oh-my-posh init pwsh --config &#x27;D:\Scoop\apps\oh-my-posh\current\themes\bubblesextra.omp.json&#x27; | Invoke-Expression</span><br><span class="line">Invoke-Expression (&amp;scoop-search --hook)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还可以安装更多powershell模块</p><ol start="4"><li>安装<code>PSReadLine</code>和 <code>PowerShellGet</code></li></ol><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Install-PackageProvider</span> <span class="literal">-Name</span> NuGet <span class="literal">-Force</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装或更新<code>PowerShellGet</code></p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Install-Module</span> <span class="literal">-Name</span> PowerShellGet <span class="literal">-Force</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Update-Module</span> <span class="literal">-Name</span> PowerShellGet</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装<code>PSReadLine</code></p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Install-Module</span> <span class="literal">-Name</span> PSReadLine <span class="literal">-AllowPrerelease</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开powershell配置文件</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">notepad <span class="variable">$PROFILE</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>添加配置，更多配置请<a href="https://github.com/PowerShell/PSReadLine/tree/master">参见</a></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Import-Module PSReadLine</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadLineOption -PredictionSource History # 设置预测文本来源为历史记录</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadlineKeyHandler -Key Tab -Function MenuComplete# 设置 Tab 键补全</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadlineKeyHandler -Key UpArrow -Function HistorySearchBackward# 设置向下键为前向搜索历史纪录</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadlineKeyHandler -Key DownArrow -Function HistorySearchForward# 设置向上键为后向搜索历史记录</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadLineKeyHandler -Key &quot;Ctrl+z&quot; -Function Undo# 设置 Ctrl+z 为撤销</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadLineKeyHandler -Key &quot;Ctrl+d&quot; -Function MenuComplete# 设置 Ctrl+d 为菜单补全和 Intellisense</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装终端图标</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Install-Module</span> <span class="literal">-Name</span> Terminal<span class="literal">-Icons</span> <span class="literal">-Repository</span> PSGallery</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开powershell配置文件</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">notepad <span class="variable">$PROFILE</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>导入终端字体</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Import-Module -Name Terminal-Icons</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用以下命令验证是否生效</p><figure class="highlight powershell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">Get-ChildItem</span> <span class="literal">-Path</span> . <span class="literal">-Force</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最终<code>Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1</code>如下：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">oh-my-posh init pwsh --config &#x27;D:\Scoop\apps\oh-my-posh\current\themes\bubblesextra.omp.json&#x27; | Invoke-Expression</span><br><span class="line">Import-Module PSReadLine</span><br><span class="line">Import-Module posh-git</span><br><span class="line">Import-Module -Name Terminal-Icons</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadLineOption -PredictionSource History</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadlineKeyHandler -Key Tab -Function MenuComplete</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadlineKeyHandler -Key UpArrow -Function HistorySearchBackward</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadlineKeyHandler -Key DownArrow -Function HistorySearchForward</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadLineKeyHandler -Key &quot;Ctrl+z&quot; -Function Undo</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadLineKeyHandler -Key &quot;Ctrl+d&quot; -Function MenuComplete</span><br><span class="line">Invoke-Expression (&amp;scoop-search --hook)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>本文资料参考：<br><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/489898732">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/489898732</a><br><a href="https://ohmyposh.dev/docs/installation/windows">https://ohmyposh.dev/docs/installation/windows</a><br><a href="https://drrany.github.io/wt/">https://drrany.github.io/wt/</a><br><a href="https://blog.antosubash.com/posts/setting-up-powershell-with-oh-my-posh-v3">https://blog.antosubash.com/posts/setting-up-powershell-with-oh-my-posh-v3</a><br><a href="https://github.com/PowerShell/PSReadLine/tree/master">https://github.com/PowerShell/PSReadLine/tree/master</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
